<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ONLY A STEP TO JESUS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu zuonin kal khat bek,
 Tu'n bang di'n suon lo ding?
 Hungin na gitloh thupha'n,
 Khunin Lalpa maah.

[V2]
 Kal khat bekin, kal khat bek in,
 Zuon in A hun ngak;
 Hungin, na gitloh thuphan,
 A vangsakna chuh mun la,
 A zahngaihna chuh niel ki'n,
 Man beia A hun piek.

[V3]
 2. Isu zuonin kal khat bek,
 Gingin, chun, hing inla;
 Lungsiet in A hun ngak zing,
 Ngaidam dinga mansa'n.

[V4]
 3. Isu zuonin kal khat bek,
 Gitloh 'pat lungsietna;
 Na lungin bang na gel em?
 Phat kin takin a bei.

[V5]
 4. Isu zuonin kal khat bek,
 Bang di'n zie gen lo ding;
 &quot;Kipak takin Hukdampa,
 Ka hinna ka hun piei&quot;</lyrics>
<hymn_number>164</hymn_number>
</song>